{"tid":183691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[西隧咁闊] 女臥底放蛇半年破援交網","createTime":"2017-04-02T09:53:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-03T06:53:00.000Z","uid":26769,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"df5cfa4ce7f60f8646727818e70417a4f6094f9a","tid":183691,"uid":26769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T09:53:45.000Z","msg":"【助養援交女】賣淫網10萬會員5年賺2千萬 卧底警拉23男女<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170402&amp;guid=56512966&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170402%26guid%3D56512966%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=BfE6afXCHr80cM3PNjd%2Fp4zu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=5ee914ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170402%26guid%3D56512966%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=c2f9a751\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170402&amp;guid=56512966&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170402/large/1491124348_873d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170402%2Flarge%2F1491124348_873d.jpg&h=2921137f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有賣淫集團以「助養」為名開設會員制網站協助男女會員進行援交活動！警方早前展開一個代號「制勝」臥底行動，以保護兒童及青少年為目的，打擊以援交為名的有組織網上非法賣淫的集團，其間探員得悉一個名為「hklovely香港少女論壇」的活躍網站，提供平台予男女會員進行性交易，並向男會員收取高昂的入會費。<br />\n<br />\n新界北總區重案組第三隊派出一男<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一女卧底探員</span></span>滲入網站收集情報及證據，至昨日開始進行拘捕行動，拘捕12男11女，合共23人，年齡介乎17至67歲。當中被捕9人為該援交網站的骨幹成員，包括網主、管理人員及提供戶口予組織取錢的人士，各人涉嫌倚靠他人賣淫維生及洗黑錢被捕，據報部分人有黑社會勝和背景。另外被捕的14名男女，包括男會員及5名提供援交的女子則涉嫌誘使他人作不道德的行為。據了解，5名援交女年齡介乎17至29歲，年紀最小的一人為無業，其餘均有正職工作，相信她們貪快錢而投身賣淫工作。<br />\n<br />\n新界北刑事部警司(行動)李桂華指該網站由2012年開始運作，會員人數達10萬，得益高達2000萬港元。行動中，警方撿獲兩部私家車，總值410萬港元，相信是由犯罪得益所購買，另外警方亦撿獲5萬港元、16部電腦、26部智能電話、相關銀行卡及文件等，其後亦凍結5個被利用或處理黑錢的戶口，拘捕行動仍然繼續。<br />\n<br />\n新界北重案組高級督察顏凱欣指該集團的收益，主要靠收取男會員高昂的入會費，然後再提供網上賣淫平台，讓援交女子可以公開招攬嫖客。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n女警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3d9eb32c810f3278493fdfdd866e80b906407b6","tid":183691,"uid":42767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T09:56:45.000Z","msg":"猶太人扮援交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0888b9df6f384f0e4ff9836c50dae45c84b1ac5","tid":183691,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T10:03:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>猶太人扮援交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又食又拎"},{"pid":"a8cae375bf914b821d48e5f8a12a2bcc38c3fe25","tid":183691,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T10:06:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>猶太人扮援交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又食又拎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3451eb7308e40b46983d95f30fb5e5acb920ff24","tid":183691,"uid":26769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T10:11:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>猶太人扮援交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n又食又拎</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔知女臥底接左幾多個客<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a44166ef5b39a587024da0432065f3fd89ad3959","tid":183691,"uid":99960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T10:15:25.000Z","msg":"男臥底食左幾多援交女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be1dd9e15c8a10970